value: India to s China, SE Asia, Sumatra, Andaman and Nicobar is.

Breeds in the Himalayas from Kuman through Assam, southeastern Tibet, and Szechwan to Hupeh, south to Burma, Yunnan and Annam. Has been taken in winter or as a wanderer in the Indian Peninsula, Hainan, Cochinchina, Malay Peninsula and Sumatra.
